Datacenter Technician

Datacenter Technician

Strong communication and interpersonal skills
Ability to work independently to complete specific tasks and meet inflexible deadlines.
Ability to work well with others and be a project leader.
Able to manage multiple priorities and projects. (Multi-tasking)

Networking and Linux Server knowledge.
Able to rack/unrack heavy equipment.

Please see Job posting at LinkedIn
